    {
      "id": "68",
      "name": "Lore",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Caribert",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 1,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "left",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/02/237301566/061f227f514e9af8ca74c1672d1f32e5_8824388314988044131.jpg"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Five hundred years ago, in the kingdom without gods, Khaenri’ah, the Five Sinners exploited the power of the Abyss and shook the foundations of the world. The Heavenly Principles destroyed Khaenri’ah and cursed the people of the kingdom. The purebloods were cursed to suffer endless physical torment and to witness the demise of everything they held dear, while the rest were transformed into monsters. A nobleman from the Royal Court, Clothar Alberich, fathered an illegitimate son with a Mondstadt woman, who they named Caribert. Because of his origin, Clothar was never able to be there by his son’s side. Caribert faced great hardship from the very moment of his birth, all due to his father’s selfish desires. When all the people of the kingdom were cursed, Clothar was cursed with immortality, and his son became a Hilichurl and fell into a coma.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "right",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2025/04/02/237301566/ad3cfbf41c685ff8f2ba7600218a5c8d_6045531549514605632.png"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "Clothar could not accept his son's condition and begged the Archons to help him, but they did not answer. Then he took Caribert to Sumeru and tried to make the Nameless Taboo Medicine of the Royal Court, which, according to the records, was imbued with the power of Sumeru's God of Wisdom and could awaken the mind from a state of deep stupor. But Alberich did not know that the previous Dendro Archon, Rukkhadevata, had died, and the new Archon, Kusanali, was locked in the Sanctuary of Surasthana by her subjects, so she could not help the boy. When Clothar tried to make a second dose of the medicine, he saw a Hilichurl similar to his son heading into a cave and followed it. In this cave, he met a",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": "who called himself a \"Sinner.\" Alberich was immediately overcome with a sense of awe and joy and knelt before the being. Coming out of the cave, Clothar thought with horror about bowing to the Statue of the Seven, but he had a strange feeling that something destined by fate had happened. When Clothar reached the house, he saw that his son was awake. Caribert felt like he had woken up from a long dream, where he was hiding in a small room and did not dare to leave it for all the time. When he woke up, his father told him that they had entered a fairy-tale world where there was no longer a red sky, their home, or Khaenri'ah itself. In this world, Caribert had become a monster who could not remove his mask but who would always be by his father's side.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Deciding that he must pay tribute to the \"Sinner,\" Clothar went to the cave again, but when he returned, Caribert was not home. The boy did not follow his father's orders and took off his mask to look at himself in the mirror. Unable to bear his reflection, the boy ran away from home and again returned to his previous state. When Clothar saw his son, he finally realized that the being that gave Caribert his power was not a deity and that this power came from the Abyss. He decided that with this power, Caribert could weave his destiny anew.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "italic"
                      ],
                      "text": "\"Born into abject sorrow, he shall now become the Loom of Fate.\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Related Entries:",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 4811,
                      "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/11/237301566/93cd2bc9b90c8b87b1f8cbdbe95b4b9d_705904275694017757.png",
                      "menu_id": 22,
                      "name": "Каэнри'ах",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3796,
                      "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/26/237301566/a19531bd8e93b793b79bfe1499b5b5d7_7637529122280724157.png",
